sourcesContent:
let searchListContainer = {
  display: "flex",
  width: "80%",
  height: "93vh",
  margin: "15px 0px 0px 15px"
}

let phoneListContainer = {
  height: "30px",
  display: "flex",
  marginTop: "15px",
  paddingBottom: "5px",
  width: "calc(60vw - 28px)"
}

let phoneListContainerMAC = {
  cursor: "pointer",
  fontSize: "19px",
  textAlign: "center",
  height: "30px",
  minWidth: "200px",
  color: "white",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 5px",
}

let phoneListContainerInfo = {
  height: "28px",
  width: "100%",
  borderStyle: "solid",
  borderLeftStyle: "none",
  borderWidth: "1px",
  borderColor: "#4382BC",
}

let phoneListContainerItems = {
  listStyleType: "none",
  display: "flex",
  marginTop: "2px",
  textAlign: "center"
}

let phoneListContainerItem = {
  fontSize: "17px",
  width: "20%",
  marginRight: "12px",
  textTransform: "capitalize",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  textOverflow: "ellipsis"
}

export {
  phoneListContainer,
  phoneListContainerMAC,
  phoneListContainerInfo,
  phoneListContainerItems,
  phoneListContainerItem,
  searchListContainer
}
